snippet.title: Amber Heard JOINING Margot Robbie's Pirates of The Caribbean Spin-Off Movie? - A SICK JOKE!
snippet.description:
There's loads of rumors floating around the internet that Amber Heard is in talks to join Margot Robbie's Pirates of the Caribbean female Spin-off movie. That would be the biggest slap to the face imaginable, but maybe good? Let's discuss! Let me know what you think and make sure to subscribe to the channel for more content!!
